<P>&nbsp;</P>
<P>For the serious stuff (this is all just based on my experience - although I am tempted to say EVERYTHING is VERY IMPORTANT to me)</P>
<P>CLASS: shaman</P>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>HP: Very important<BR>Mana: Very important<BR>Endurance: Not important<BR>AC: Important</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>HP Regen: Very important<BR>Mana Regen: Very important<BR>Endurance Regen: Not important</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Strength: Not important<BR>Stamina: Important<BR>Agility: Not important<BR>Dexterity: Not important<BR>Charisma: Not important<BR>Intelligence: Not important<BR>Wisdom: Important</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Cold Resist: Important<BR>Disease Resist: Important<BR>Poison Resist: Important<BR>Magic Resist: Important<BR>Fire Resist: Important</DIV>
<DIV>(all resists are good, of course)</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Attack: Not important<BR>Delay: Not important<BR>Damage: Not important<BR>Range: Not important<BR>Haste: Not important</DIV>
<DIV>(I know that some shaman enjoy meleeing, I am not one of them)<BR></DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Combat Effects: <BR>Shielding: Important</DIV>
<DIV>Stun Resist: Very important (to me, I hate being stunned)<BR>Strikethrough: Not important (I confess to not being sure what this is)<BR>Spell Shield: Important<BR>Avoidance: Important<BR>Accuracy: Not important <BR>DOT Shielding: Important</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Skill Mods: <BR>Click Effects: Very important (to me, I adore click effects, love love love love)<BR>Proc Effects: Not important (fun as a toy to me, although I still do love my old VP snare spear)<BR>Worn Effects: Very important<BR>Focus Effects: VERY IMPORTANT - shaman are really really hurt in this area since we need so many different kinds of foci to be effective&nbsp;- I consider most focus effects MUST HAVES - spell haste, extended buff duration, extended detrimental, spell range, improved heal, mana preservatrion. Improved nuke and dot power are a lot of fun for me. One of the reasons I quit playing so much was the feeling of being overwhelmed at having to replace ALL my focus effects and the domino effect it would have as I lost functionality to replace gear.<BR></DIV><p>Message Edited by Gloriana-EM on <span class=date_text>07-06-2006</span> <span class=time_text>12:49 PM</span>
				
